name: The Nightmare’s Nightmare
description:
A dark abstract piece with rectilinear vignetting reveals a glimpse of repeated, monstrous forms. Saturated reds and pinks in the center of the piece flow into magenta then purple then blue flickering at the edge like some kind of Hawking radiation of transdimensional madness.

2732x2048 pixel PNG

Minted August 10th, 2021. Verify via Twitter account @tormential and/or Instagram account @_tormential_ and/or tormential.tez
